message.body: I'm out front of ur work
I'm home. Won't be there till 5. I can meet you before, though. Need to do a lunch walk for Zoey at 12:30.
Are you doing the lunch walk or am I?
I'll get the key from you when you come in to work ok? I gota go do some stuff
Ok, sounds good. I'll be there a little before 5. Zoey will need her dinner walk around 5:30-6:00.
Just got to work. I don't normally check my phone during my shift, so come on in.
How's it going over there? Is Zoey being nice to you?
She's fine we're just going for our night walk now
Ah, nice. Just got home. Thanks for staying with Zoey tonight. I needed a break and have to get some stuff here before tomorrow.
No problem. Get your stuff done. This is the biggest tv I have ever seen
Yeah, it's kind of massive. Most of our sits have big TV's and large homes. A different way of living in Phillyz
You are taking over the Zoe walks this afternoon, correct?
Yep. What time did you last walk her?
815 or so. She took her meds too.
Excellent. I'll be leaving the house for my brunch shift tomorrow & Sunday around 8:45am. You can do her lunch walks on Sat and Sun anytime between 12-1:30.
